<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>How to Use This Website</title>
    <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet"> <!-- Link to your main CSS file -->
    <style>
        /* Modern styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Merriweather', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .step {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .step h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .step p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .navigation-buttons {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .navigation-buttons a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #3498db; /* Primary color */
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .navigation-buttons a:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9; /* Darker shade for hover */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>How to Use This Website</h1>

        <div class="step">
            <h2>Step 1: Explore the Homepage</h2>
            <p>Start by exploring our homepage where you'll find an overview of our main features and latest updates.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h2>Step 2: Check Out Our Features</h2>
            <p>Navigate to the features page to learn more about what we offer and how you can benefit from our services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h2>Step 3: Submit A website</h2>
            <p>Showcase your expertise to the world.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
            <h2>Step 4: Start Using the Tools</h2>
            <p>Once you're logged in, start using our tools and features to enhance your experience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="navigation-buttons">
            <a href="/" class="back-button">Back to Home</a>
            
        </div>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size:2rem; color: #555; padding: 20px 0;">
            Made with <span style="color: red;">&#10084;&#65039;</span> by Ujjwal
        </p>
    
    </div>
</body>
</html>
